{"tid":133312,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【急尋】16歲少年北角失蹤 警呼籲巿民留意","createTime":"2017-02-24T13:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T00:11:39.000Z","uid":51598,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e38d629ec3b545db0fd21ca365bb96b3424d635d","tid":133312,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7gx8fltc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7gx8fltc&h=694ec279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n16歲少年Mohammad Shahzad前日下午離開其位於北角英皇道的住所後便告失蹤，其家人延至昨日向警方報案。他身高約1.52米，體重約60公斤，中等身材，圓面型，深色皮膚及蓄短直黑髮。他最後露面時攜有一個黑色背包。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何人如有該失蹤男童的消息或曾見過他，請致電2860 1040、9886 0034或電郵至rmpu-hki@police.gov.hk與港島總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"914d10258b1196fdc50a5e057b5734b2139bc287","tid":133312,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ee8c0996d6d3c5adb5dcba9092df93cf52c498","tid":133312,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"16歲咁矮？<br />\n畀著我去咗自殺啦&hellip;"},{"pid":"d0944287256e7a673a81bf05ca383eca56c761f4","tid":133312,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"笑得咁開心即係無事啦"},{"pid":"d45cc9aea2da70de3faa96f1686918ab7e7283be","tid":133312,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"1.52 16歲"},{"pid":"a65659d0a910e40dbc0a4cbacb62f98e915c9ec5","tid":133312,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑得咁開心即係無事啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a26d6d7835cc47f5b25a839b521861eb8330479","tid":133312,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"屌呢d樣一街都係 點認呀"},{"pid":"3f7261